lenders.name: Cems Club Helsinki
lenders.loan_because: CEMS Club Helsinki wants to make a difference!
lenders.occupational_info:
Founded in 1999, the CEMS Club Helsinki promotes CEMS-awareness within the Finnish business community. The Club also seeks to create and maintain working relations with the CEMS interest groups and to do its best to make Aalto better known internationally, and especially within the CEMS network.

In addition, the CEMS Club Helsinki organizes numerous activities throughout the year such as networking events with corporate partners, company excursions and social events. Aalto Cemsers and alumni, visiting CEMS students and everybody interested in the program are welcome to enjoy the warm atmosphere of the activities.
